## <img height="24" src="https://img.icons8.com/fluent/48/000000/about.png"/> About
> <img align="right" height="120" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/FluffyMak4ic/Fur.Bot/FoxsomeRework/data/logo.jpg"/>
> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/FurBot-1.0r1-red?style=flat-square&logo=data:image/png;base64,"/>
>
> * **FurBot** is a bot written for the
>  `VKontakte`  social network in
>  order to pump out pictures
>  from the `e926.net` website.
> <a href="https://vk.com/furbot"><img height="32" src="https://icon-icons.com/icons2/832/PNG/64/vk_icon-icons.com_66681.png"/></a>

> <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/pipenv/locked/dependency-version/FluffyMak4ic/Fur.Bot/vk-api/FoxsomeRework?color=red&style=flat-square&logo=vk&logoColor=white"/>
> 
> * **FurBot** fully based on Python Vkontakte API
